nner" href="..com/healthcare-solutions/advanced-care-in-the-home/" target="_blank"><div class="four-column-hover"><div class="icon"><img src="https://www.scphealth.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Advanced_Care_Inhome_icon-1.png" alt="SCP Health - Advanced Care in the Home." ></div><h4>Advanced Care<br> in the Home</h4><p>An extension of your institution, our virtual clinical care teams help health systems and hospitals provide high-quality, acute hospital patient care beyond the four walls of the hospital and into patients' homes.</p><span class="btn-link">Learn More</span></div></a></div><div class="four-column-item cell-lg-3 cell-md-6"><a class="four-column-inner" href="..com/healthcare-solutions/clinical-integration/" target="_blank"><div class="four-column-hover"><div class="icon"><img src="https://www.scphealth.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/SCP_Icons-40_Clinical_Integration_Magenta.svg" alt="SCP Health - Clinical Integration." ></div><h4>Clinical<br> Integration</h4><p>Helping hospitals and health systems drive transformation in effectiveness, efficiency, and growth, our clinical and operational experts help align and integrate processes and optimizes your financial spend across emergency, hospital, and critical care medicine.</p><span class="btn-link">Learn More</span></div></a></div></div></div>
